            "answer_text": "Should I assume you meant to type :doesn\u2019t\u201d? The reason is simple - they don\u2019t have to. That would mean entering the market for consumer-grade PCs which is horrifically competitive and with profit margins you can barely see. They are making a profit on Macs without having to enter the MMA-level market of $500 PCs. I would personally hate to have to be in that market because every night I would have nightmares of one of my competitors suddenly finding a way to shave ten cents off the price of their machines and eating our lunch. ",
