            "answer_text": "If they are using older Macs, clearly there isn\u2019t a problem: they simply use older Macs. Because they still work fine for them. This is why I\u2019m happy to drop money on new Macs: I know they\u2019ll last. I bought a G4 Sawbuck Tower in the late 1990s and it strictly still runs to this day though I don\u2019t use it because I can\u2019t run the latest MacOS on it. My G4 Mac Cube also still runs fine. This is why you buy value. And why buying old Macs can be a reason value for people on budgets. ",
